National Council of Pronvices: Questions to the Deputy President, Virtual Media Platform, 16th March 2022, 14:00 CAPE TOWN - Deputy President David Mabuza is answering questions in the National Council of Provinces. Among others, Mabuza will be asked about the government's position regarding the Russian invasion of Ukraine but the bulk of the questions he is facing are about domestic issues. READ: Mabuza: State capture report a positive step in corruption fight These include the pace of land reform, the provision of quality water to communities and efforts to address criminal activities involving foreign nationals.